_sText:
This version of the map is optimized. You'll notice that many things are smaller. Version 1 is about 40 MB. I managed to get that down to about 24 MB.  

This is pretty much a random b-hop map I made when I was bored.
There is about 7 secrets in this map, try to find them all. ;)
I've learned many things by making this map that I can use in future ideas.
I didn't run VIS because it would take about 2 days to compile. (I'm a noob mapper.)
This is pretty much my first serious map.
All the people who helped with this map are at the end of the map written on the wall.


I hope you enjoy!
